BlueFox Mobile Gaming Privacy Policy
UPDATED ON: August 28, 2020
BlueFox Mobile Gaming (hereinafter “BlueFox Mobile Gaming” or “I” or “Me” or ‘’Mine’’)  have created this Privacy Policy to inform you of BlueFox Mobile Gaming's policies regarding how I use, collect and disclose your Personal Information when you use BlueFox Mobile Gamins's Service. BlueFox Mobile Gaming is an individual gaming developer, focused primarily on building fun games for android devices. I am located in Florida, United States and I have created games like Space Escape Adventures and Pinball Legends.
I will use and share your information only as described in this Privacy Policy.
The latest version of this privacy policy is available at bluefoxmobilegaming.webflow.io/privacy-policy. Your continued use of the Service is subject to the latest privacy policy.
‍
Data Collection
The below describes the data I collect and the reasons  why I collect it.
When I say that I collect data for "Analytics", I mean that the data is used and collected for marketing and statistical purposes so that I can improve the Service and future services .
BlueFox Mobile Gaming may view your data, including "Analytics" data, only when:
the Game is in the test, pre-release "beta" phase, or
it is necessary to execute a support request by you, or
it is necessary to investigate a technical issue, or
it is necessary to investigate cheating, fraud or threats towards the security and functioning of the Service or its users.
The personal data that I review is stated below:
Gameplay statistics
What you write in google reviews
App usage events such as achievement, leaderboards
Device model and characteristics (e.g. display size, android version)
Receipts of in-app purchases
Technical errors and crashes
‍
Data from Advertising Companies
Advertisement platforms such as facebook ads, may provide me with additional data about you. This data may include personal information, such as your gender, your interests or your broad age range. This data sharing is governed by the privacy policy of the platform where the advertisement is shown. I may connect this data with your profile to better understand the users who use my game.
‍
Sharing Data with Third Parties
To make available for you the best player experience possible, I have integrated Google Play Services, to have access to leaderboards and achievements (to sign in using Google Sign-in feature). Know that this data is not collected by me in any way, this is stored on your device, and it is only needed to provide you with leaderboards and achievements. People who do not desire to login with their google play account, are still able to play the game.
The app does use third party services that may collect information used to identify you.
Link to privacy policy of third party service providers used by the app
AdMob
Unity
AdColony
GooglePlay Services
‍
Service Providers
I may employ third-party companies and individuals due to the following reasons:
To facilitate the Service of BlueFox Mobile Gaming;
To provide the Service on my behalf;
To perform Service-related services; or
To assist me in analyzing how BlueFox Mobile Gaming Service is used.
I want to inform users of this Service that these third parties have access to your Personal Information. The reason is to perform the tasks assigned to them on my behalf. However, they are obligated not to disclose or use the information for any other purpose.
‍
Security
I value your trust in providing BlueFox Mobile Gaming your Personal Information, thus I am striving to use commercially acceptable means of protecting it. But remember that no method of transmission over the internet, or method of electronic storage is 100% secure and reliable, and I cannot guarantee its absolute security. Please remember to not share your gmail account with anyone.
‍
Age Limits
BlueFox Mobile Gaming has created Pinball Legends and Space Escape Adventures for Mix Audiences. As i stated above it is not mandatory for you to use Google Sign In, and Google Play Services to play my game. It is just an added value to improve game experience with leaderboards and achievements.
‍
Changes to This Privacy Policy
I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, you are advised to review this page periodically for any changes. I will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
This policy is effective as of 2020-08-25
